'''Zulfiqar Ali''' (born 1965) was the mayor of [[Rochdale]], in the north west of England. He was born in [[Bradford]].  He took office in 2010.<ref>http://www.libdems.org.uk/zulfiqar_ali</ref>

Ali is the  chairman, [[Reach BCS]], Rochdale, Lancashire. In 2008, he was awarded the [[Queen's Award for Enterprise Promotion (2008)|Queen's Award for Enterprise Promotion]].<ref>https://www.thegazette.co.uk/London/issue/58673/supplement/4/data.pdf</ref>

